      "date": "2022-06-09 07:07:02.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1\n\n(1 comment)\n\nI think the actual problem is that we are missing a connection flag like 'OBD_CONNECT2_ENCRYPT_NAME'. If server side does not have this flag, client side should always use NULL encryption for names.\n\nI will push a patch to add this new connection flag.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
